OL,4,CBarbican Centre branded 'inherently
OL,5,Cracist' by current and former staff
OL,6, The Barbican Centre, Europe's largest
OL,7, multi-arts venue, has been accused of
OL,8, being "inherently racist" in a dossier
OL,9, compiled by current and former staff.
OL,11,FBarbican Stories, released on Thursday,
OL,12,Fcontains "first-hand and witnessed
OL,13,Faccounts of racism and discrimination".
OL,15,FResponding to the claims, The Barbican
OL,16,Fsaid it was "shocked and saddened" and
OL,17,Fhad launched an investigation.
OL,19,FCopies of the anonymously-written book
OL,20,Fhave been sent to the London venue's
OL,21,Fbosses.
